name: MDBList Ratings
overview: MDBList Ratings is a Jellyfin plugin that automatically fetches ratings from MDBList using a media item’s TMDb ID, writes selected ratings into Jellyfin’s built-in rating fields, and (optionally) enhances the Jellyfin Web UI with an “All ratings” panel showing every rating MDBList provides.
